2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家29歲<br />\n淨剩係諗住點搵多啲錢<br />\n早早享受退休生活<br />\n做個孤獨的美食家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9adec7d22350218ffa0426f6e7a3a73f148943d","tid":1073702,"uid":55533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"286daae61cef8fd17e9c0ca822e22e0ddf504a20","tid":1073702,"uid":54387,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T02:47:41.000Z","msg":"39A0<br />\n人又老, 樓又買唔到<br />\n<br />\n只係得死呢條路"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T03:24:49.000Z","msg":"享受生活<br />\n活在當下<br />\n<img src=\"https://fongbao.files.wordpress.com/2012/04/e5ada4e78da8e79a84e7be8ee9a39fe5aeb6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffongbao.files.wordpress.com%2F2012%2F04%2Fe5ada4e78da8e79a84e7be8ee9a39fe5aeb6.jpg&h=0bc4da36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不被世間和社會所束縛，幸福地填飽肚子的時候，短時間內變得隨心所欲，變得自由。誰也不打擾，毫不費神地吃東西的這種孤高行為。這種行為才是平等地賦予現代人的最大程度的治癒。"},{"pid":"16368f07015d3092e3c279c971e5d8262b2a4de8","tid":1073702,"uid":61105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T03:36:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c171ec91575004ec168901c556b112076fd53ff6","tid":1073702,"uid":172041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f28c95c301f56e03033ada54d7b3ca7f5a3a94e","tid":1073702,"uid":118628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"353f06f22ed6815d3b2cbf237c90c81d62e9ea0f","tid":1073702,"uid":172041,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7afea53f331af3b924d18643bc7f7fa9212f5c6b","tid":1073702,"uid":118628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T02:19:06.000Z","msg":"DKLM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T02:20:20.000Z","msg":"諗下失敗原因係乜<br />\n唔好乜都用果6個字黎做理由<br />\n雖然會有呢d因素係入面<br />\n不過一定唔係全部"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T02:21:56.000Z","msg":"SBT<br />\n<br />\n點都好, 多謝鼓勵"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20